  <div class="textblock">
    <p>
      For searching the Pfam database <a href="http://hmmer.janelia.org/" target="_blank">HMMER</a> (current version 2.3.2, October 2003) is used. HMMER allows for sensitive searching in a database of protein family's consensus supplied as a profile hidden Markov model version [{'hmmer'|ref}]. 
      <br/>
      For our purpose the Pfam database was restricted to membrane protein families to allow faster searches. To achieve this the Pfam <a href="http://pfam.sanger.ac.uk/search/keyword" target="_blank">keyword search</a> was used to generate a reduced database of entries predominantly containing membrane proteins.
    </p>

